micro_product.name: Dream Away - Final Sale
micro_product.description:
The Dream Away pullover comes in a rich burgundy color that you'll love each time that you catch a glimpse of your reflection. Unlike a conventional pullover, you can now enjoy real comfort and movement, with the soft hand feel of long fiber cotton, 6-way stretch, and Buttercloth's trademark double-sided construction. Equally important, you'll look amazing in our signature tailored fit. Step with confidence into a meeting or out to a dinner party with coworkers, looking every inch the dapper gentleman that you are.
Model is 6'2" with a 40" Chest and is wearing size M, Regular fit

micro_product.name: Men's The Legacy
micro_product.description:
Description
Easy to slip on high tops that can be dressed up like boots, worn like sneakers, and feel like comfy socks.  Designed with a natural toe box, weather proof toe cap, and an ankle hugging upper, these versatile shoes are made for going anywhere and doing anything.

Wide, Natural Toe Box
Easy to Slip On without Untying/Unlacing
Rubber toe cap keeps your toes dry in rainy weather
Soft ankle hugging Upper
Moisture Wicking and Breathable Materials (For wearing with or without socks)
Washable & Dries Quick
Packs Flat (Perfect for any bag or your travels)
Made Sustainably with 100% Post-Consumer Recycled Threads

Minimalist sole with 3-5 mm heel to toe drop



 
Fitting
Fits true to size.  Half sizes should size up.
If you need more help with sizing or fitting, please email us at contact@suavs.com.
 
Materials

Premium Digital Knit Upper made from Post-Consumer Recycled Water Bottles.
Soft Rubber toe cap.
Cotton Laces.
Removable & washable foam insole lined with micro towel for moisture absorption.
Flexible, stitched rubber sole bends right along with your feet's movements.
Vegan Friendly.
